{"tid":418582,"cid":30,"subCid":0,"title":"唔做狗公正戇鳩","createTime":"2017-09-29T16:20:13.000Z","updateTime":"2017-10-06T16:26:56.000Z","uid":389,"like":6,"dislike":1,"uniUserReply":10,"replies":[{"pid":"092d628c719fb9180b419b787643d72b38ecfe82","tid":418582,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:20:13.000Z","msg":"為左所謂既聲譽，為左唔比人叫狗公<br />\n我竟然傻到連私人訊息都唔send<br />\n淨係被動收msg<br />\n十年朋友<br />\n最後竟然唔夠人搶<br />\n重要比個男既話係狗公要食淨既餸頭餸尾餵我<br />\n話我不懷好意接近個女仔<br />\n<br />\n<br />\n我亦根本唔可以講個男仔壞話咪先變小人<br />\n我點解可以戇鳩到咁<br />\n<br />\n竟然自己退場<br />\n重要比人屈返係狗公<br />\n咁當初點解要淡出<br />\n點解到頭來我會變左做狗公<br />\n早知今日，當初就應該真係狗衝<br />\n<br />\n一句狗公，足以KO我<br />\n完"},{"pid":"6efa9e9eb3375dcacd7eb0580fe5e0df104b00ac","tid":418582,"uid":41737,"like":0,"dislike":1,"score":-1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:24:01.000Z","msg":"此回覆已被刪除"},{"pid":"bbd07282c38ab224b46ddd32fc4859df4a19f376","tid":418582,"uid":59569,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:24:50.000Z","msg":"yes"},{"pid":"80d628077633f64a5f73c6ba0e53c8cb8fd679cf","tid":418582,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:27:06.000Z","msg":"閹割得太耐<br />\n已經唔記得左獵食既本能係點"},{"pid":"99f21be88ed0fbd2014d6c088c6502de56bb0eb2","tid":418582,"uid":94452,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:38:48.000Z","msg":"出口咬人先個個永遠大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"5150355215828091b7f11740dcaef613971b86bd","tid":418582,"uid":389,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T16:43:23.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出口咬人先個個永遠大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n我以我俾人咬到玩撚完"},{"pid":"9bff4ac8fd479f42307ef530b5fa07ac02e8e4a9","tid":418582,"uid":77820,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:10:43.000Z","msg":"做狗公都要睇下自己咩質素<br />\n靚仔=未來男朋友<br />\n柒頭=狗公"},{"pid":"89489145c430e3fabf2eada641bcb9f838acd926","tid":418582,"uid":80162,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:12:19.000Z","msg":"呢個世界就係咁狗<br />\n你唔做狗公係唔會溝到女架"},{"pid":"8c39b3035a7b6ba9eb1a2e09cdb2e0d67333affe","tid":418582,"uid":90133,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:13:45.000Z","msg":"狗公 正仆街"},{"pid":"54bbd6f851fea216c2a9be0013e152bfb0c052ad","tid":418582,"uid":32442,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-29T17:32:45.000Z","msg":"<blockquote>出口咬人先個個永遠大哂<img src=\"/assets/faces/mf/bouncer.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /></blockquote><br />\n唔係既 呢類人個名會好臭<br />\n稍為了解下都知咩事  學識聽完佢9up就算 信一成都比多<br />\n吸引到既都係d一係蠢一係犯賤既女仔  無意義"},{"pid":"242bcafa735cdf29317e533d288fc4f16f6a2185","tid":418582,"uid":131064,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:23:56.000Z","msg":"狗公石丸果然係狗公"},{"pid":"0d0d76424cedde7f11550c932525984174488e92","tid":418582,"uid":83998,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-10-06T16:26:56.000Z","msg":"十年一早fdzone左啦師兄"}]}